<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>pokepost — Dashboard</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-white to-green-100 min-h-screen font-sans text-gray-800">
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-20 flex justify-between items-center px-6 py-4 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm border-b border-green-100">

    <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700">
      Pokepost 🍃
    </h1>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <a href="/profile" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition shadow-md text-sm">
        Profile
      </a>
      <form method="get" action="/logout" class="inline">
        <input type="submit" value="Logout" class="px-4 py-2 bg-emerald-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-600 transition shadow-md cursor-pointer text-sm" />
      </form>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main Feed -->
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-2 sm:px-6 py-6">
    <!-- Posts Feed -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-700 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>📚</span>
        Community Adventures
      </h3>

      <div class="grid gap-6 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

        <!-- Post 1 -->
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-white/80">
          <!-- Post Header -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-900 transition-colors line-clamp-2">
              My First Legendary Encounter! ⚡
            </h3>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-200 via-green-300 to-emerald-200"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">
            After months of searching, I finally encountered Zapdos in the wild! The battle was intense, but with some strategic thinking and a lot of patience, I managed to catch this incredible Electric-type legendary. The feeling was absolutely electrifying! ⚡🎉
          </p>
          <!-- Author Info -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <img src="/images/uploads/profile1.jpg" alt="ash_trainer" class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full object-cover border border-emerald-200" />
            <p class="text-emerald-600 text-sm font-medium">
              @ash_trainer
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Engagement Stats -->
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-pink-50 rounded-full border border-red-100">
              <span class="text-red-500">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                24 likes
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Actions and Date -->
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-3 border-t border-emerald-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <a href="/like/1" class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-sm font-medium">
                <span>👍</span>
                Like
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>📅</span>
              Sun Jul 13 2025
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 2 -->
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-white/80">
          <!-- Post Header -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-900 transition-colors line-clamp-2">
              Gym Battle Victory! 🏆
            </h3>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-200 via-green-300 to-emerald-200"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">
            Just defeated the Rock-type gym with my Water-type team! Starmie's Hydro Pump was absolutely devastating against their Onix. Sometimes type advantages really do make all the difference in battle strategy. 💧⭐
          </p>
          <!-- Author Info -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <img src="/images/uploads/profile2.jpg" alt="misty_water" class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full object-cover border border-emerald-200" />
            <p class="text-emerald-600 text-sm font-medium">
              @misty_water
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Engagement Stats -->
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-pink-50 rounded-full border border-red-100">
              <span class="text-red-500">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                18 likes
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Actions and Date -->
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-3 border-t border-emerald-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <a href="/like/2" class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-sm font-medium">
                <span>👍</span>
                Like
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>📅</span>
              Sun Jul 13 2025
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 3 -->
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-white/80">
          <!-- Post Header -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-900 transition-colors line-clamp-2">
              Shiny Hunting Success! ✨
            </h3>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-200 via-green-300 to-emerald-200"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">
            After 847 encounters, I finally found a shiny Geodude! The golden coloring is absolutely beautiful. The patience required for shiny hunting really tests your dedication as a trainer, but moments like these make it all worthwhile! 🌟⛰️
          </p>
          <!-- Author Info -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <img src="/images/uploads/profile3.jpg" alt="brock_rock" class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full object-cover border border-emerald-200" />
            <p class="text-emerald-600 text-sm font-medium">
              @brock_rock
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Engagement Stats -->
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-pink-50 rounded-full border border-red-100">
              <span class="text-red-500">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                42 likes
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Actions and Date -->
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-3 border-t border-emerald-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <a href="/like/3" class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-sm font-medium">
                <span>👍</span>
                Like
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>📅</span>
              Sat Jul 12 2025
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Post 4 -->
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-white/80">
          <!-- Post Header -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-900 transition-colors line-clamp-2">
              Evolution Day! 🎉
            </h3>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-200 via-green-300 to-emerald-200"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">
            My Ekans finally evolved into Arbok today! We've been training together for months, and seeing this transformation happen is such an emotional moment. The bond between trainer and Pokémon grows stronger with each milestone. 🐍💜
          </p>
          <!-- Author Info -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <img src="/images/uploads/profile4.jpg" alt="team_rocket_jessie" class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full object-cover border border-emerald-200" />
            <p class="text-emerald-600 text-sm font-medium">
              @team_rocket_jessie
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Engagement Stats -->
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-pink-50 rounded-full border border-red-100">
              <span class="text-red-500">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                31 likes
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Actions and Date -->
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-3 border-t border-emerald-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <a href="/like/4" class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-50 hover:bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-sm font-medium">
                <span>👍</span>
                Like
              </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>📅</span>
              Sat Jul 12 2025
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Load More Button -->
      <div class="text-center py-8">
        <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-green-400 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:brightness-110 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-400 active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mx-auto" id="loadMoreBtn">
          <span id="loadMoreText">Load More Adventures</span>
          <span id="loadMoreSpinner" class="hidden animate-spin h-5 w-5 border-2 border-white border-t-green-400 rounded-full"></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="mt-24 px-6 py-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-200 via-green-200 to-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-t border-emerald-100 shadow-inner text-center text-gray-600 text-sm rounded-t-xl">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-3 text-emerald-600 font-semibold">
      <span class="animate-bounce">🍃</span>
      <span>Pokepost — Made with love for Pokémon trainers
      </span>
      <span class="animate-bounce">🍃</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-1">
      Pokepost - Share your adventures!✨
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-400">
      © <span id="current-year"></span> Pokepost. Gotta share 'em all!
    </p>
  </footer>
  <script>
    document.getElementById('current-year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();

    // Responsive image fix for post avatars
    document.querySelectorAll('img[alt]').forEach(img => {
      img.classList.add('w-8', 'h-8', 'sm:w-6', 'sm:h-6');
    });

    // Load More button spinner simulation
    document.getElementById('loadMoreBtn').addEventListener('click', function() {
      document.getElementById('loadMoreText').textContent = 'Loading...';
      document.getElementById('loadMoreSpinner').classList.remove('hidden');
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.getElementById('loadMoreText').textContent = 'Load More Adventures';
        document.getElementById('loadMoreSpinner').classList.add('hidden');
      }, 1200);
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>